  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <lg xml:id="TolC269">
          <l>ellē <app><lem wit="#Cēṉā #Nacc #Tey">yilakkam</lem><rdg wit="#Iḷam">viḷakkam</rdg></app>.</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/165/mode/1up">165</ref>.</p>
      <p>
varalāṟu:
      </p>
      <p>
itu,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC269-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘elvaḷai’</l>
        <trailer>[puṟam – 24]</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa varum.  (21)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n216/mode/1up">213</ref>.</p>
      <p>
elleṉpatu uriccoṉīrmaittāyiṉum, āciriyar iṭaic collāka ōtiṉamaiyāṉ, iṭaiccolleṉṟu kōṭum.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC269-Cena-cit1">
        <l>‘elvaḷai’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa elleṉpatu ilaṅkutaṟkaṇ vantavāṟu.
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/296/mode/1up">296</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/297/mode/1up">297</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ituvumatu.
      </p>
      <p>
(i-ḷ) ellē ilakkam – elleṉṉuñ col viḷaṅkutaṟ poruṇmaiyai yuṇarttu meṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
(u–m)
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC269-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>elvaḷai yemmoṭu nīvariṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉavarum.  <num xml:lang="en">(21)</num>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n182/mode/1up">175</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n183/mode/1up">176</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ituvumatu.
      </p>
      <p>
i–ḷ.: ― el eṉpatu ilaṅkutal kuṟittu varum. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u–m ―
      </p>
      <p>
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC269-Tey-cit1">
        <l>elvaḷai</l>
        <trailer>(puṟam. 24)</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
ilaṅkuvaḷai. itu uriccollaṉṟō eṉiṉ, atu kuṟaiccollāki niṟkum. itu kuṟaiyiṉṟi niṟṟaliṉ, iṭaiccollāyiṟṟu.     [21]
      </p>
    </body>
